result.title: Can't download complete problem set in gyms
result.content:
When I try to download the problem set pdf file in some gym, this message appears: 'Can't download contest descriptor from external storage. Are you sure you have at least one contest release?' Is there anything I could do to fix it or it is some kind of a general problem?

Update Now it works fine. I don't know why, I didn't change a thing.
